ExecDesc.value: CA ERwin Web Portal ConfigServiceProvider Information Disclosure

EngDesc.value: An information disclosure vulnerability exists in CA ERwin Web Portal. This vulnerability is due to lack of authentication and insufficient input validation in the ConfigServiceProvider servlet when processing HTTP requests. By sending crafted HTTP requests to the target system, a remote unauthenticated attacker can leverage this vulnerability to view the contents of arbitrary XML files on a target system, including XML files which store database credentials.
